snippet.title: (Walkthrough) Lego Rock Raiders - 1 - Driller Night!
snippet.description:
Mission 1 of 25

Hello all, and welcome to the first instalment of a new walkthrough series I'm doing. This is the first time I've done something like this, so this is very much an experimental run, but I hope you lot enjoy, and please feel free to leave any thoughts you might have below.
